---
layout: default
title: "Global Calc Hub | Financial Tools & Professional Calculators"
description: "Access a suite of free tools online, including a precise compound interest calculator, percentage calculator for money, and universal unit converter for global unit conversions."
---
<main class="pt-20 pb-20 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto flex-grow w-full">
    
    <!-- AdSense Leaderboard Placeholder -->
    <div class="w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto h-[90px] border-2 border-dashed border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-400 text-sm mb-12 rounded-xl hidden md:flex">
        AdSense Placement (728x90)
    </div>

    <section class="mb-16 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold font-headline mb-4 tracking-tight">Ethereal <span class="text-primary">Precision.</span></h1>
        <p class="text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">Your primary source for **professional calculators** and **free tools online**. Fast, accurate, and designed for daily use.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Calculators Grid -->
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-20">
        <!-- Tool Card 1: Compound Interest -->
        <a href="{{ '/compound-interest.html' | relative_url }}" class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-xl shadow-blue-900/5 border border-slate-100 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform block">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary mb-4 block">payments</span>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-headline mb-2">Compound Interest Calculator</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Visualize the **compound interest formula** in action. Calculate future wealth and growth for your long-term **investment** goals.</p>
        </a>

        <!-- Tool Card 2: Percentage Calculator -->
        <a href="{{ '/percentage.html' | relative_url }}" class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-xl shadow-blue-900/5 border border-slate-100 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform block">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary mb-4 block">percent</span>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-headline mb-2">Percentage Calculator</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">A dedicated **percentage calculator for money**, discounts, and price **increases**. Get instant results for any math problem.</p>
        </a>

        <!-- Tool Card 3: Unit Converter -->
        <a href="{{ '/unit-converter.html' | relative_url }}" class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-xl shadow-blue-900/5 border border-slate-100 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform block">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary mb-4 block">straighten</span>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-headline mb-2">Universal Unit Converter</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Handle **global unit conversions** instantly. A versatile **unit converter for weight**, length, and temperature across all systems.</p>
        </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Latest Article Section (Featured Insight) -->
    {% assign latest_post = site.posts.first %}
    {% if latest_post %}
    <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-20">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-headline">Latest Financial Insights</h2>
            <a href="{{ '/blog.html' | relative_url }}" class="text-primary font-bold flex items-center gap-1 hover:underline">
                Explore Blog <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <a href="{{ latest_post.url | relative_url }}" class="bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all group flex flex-col md:flex-row shadow-xl shadow-blue-900/5">
            <div class="md:w-1/2 h-64 md:h-auto overflow-hidden">
                {% if latest_post.image %}
                    <img src="{{ latest_post.image }}" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" alt="{{ latest_post.title }}">
                {% else %}
                    <div class="w-full h-full bg-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-300">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-8xl">{{ latest_post.icon }}</span>
                    </div>
                {% endif %}
            </div>
            <div class="p-8 md:p-12 md:w-1/2 flex flex-col justify-center">
                <span class="text-xs font-bold text-primary uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 block">{{ latest_post.tag }}</span>
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold font-headline mb-4 text-slate-900 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors leading-tight">{{ latest_post.title }}</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 mb-6 line-clamp-2">{{ latest_post.description }}</p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-slate-400">
                    <span>{{ latest_post.date | date: "%B %-d, %Y" }}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </a>
    </section>
    {% endif %}
    
    <!-- SEO Content Section (Integrating all keywords) -->
    <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-slate max-w-none border-t border-slate-100 pt-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-headline mb-6">Essential Financial Tools for a Smarter World</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            In an era of economic uncertainty, having access to reliable **financial tools** is more important than ever. Global Calc Hub was created to provide professionals and individuals with a suite of **free tools online** that simplify complex math. Whether you are looking for **financial tools for budgeting** or advanced **financial tools for investment**, our platform delivers instant results with ethereal precision.
        </p>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Precision Planning with our Compound Interest Calculator</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            Building wealth requires a deep understanding of how your money grows. Our **compound interest calculator** allows you to go beyond the basic **compound interest formula** by visualizing your potential returns over decades. It is an indispensable resource for anyone serious about their long-term financial health.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Universal Accuracy with our Unit Converter</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            From travel to international trade, **global unit conversions** are a part of our daily reality. Our **unit converter app**-style web interface makes it easy to switch between systems. Whether you need a **unit converter for weight** (KG to LBS) or a precise **unit converter in the UK** or US metric systems, we provide the accuracy you need without the clutter.
        </p>

        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            Discover why thousands of users trust our **professional calculators** for their daily needs. From the simplest **percentage calculator** tasks to complex financial forecasting, Global Calc Hub is your ultimate destination for precision calculation.
        </p>
    </article>
</main>
